Set the level of detail when rendering spheres.


### syntax

~~~ python
sphereDetail(ures, vres)
sphereDetail(res)
~~~

### parameters

ures | number of "slices" in sphere
vres | number of "stacks" in sphere
res  | number of "slices" and "stacks" in sphere


### examples

#### change number of slices


<%= vroom_example_image "rendering", "sphere-detail", "change-number-of-slices.png" %>


~~~ python
def display():
   lighting(False)

   translateX(-3)
   sphere(2.0)

   translateX(6)
   color(green)
   sphereDetail(24, 12)
   sphere(2.0)
~~~

