#### resolution comparison


<%= vroom_example_image "rendering", "sphere-detail", "resolution-comparison.png" %>


~~~ python
def display():
   lighting(False)
   resolution = 6
   translateX(-8)

   for i in range(9):
      sphereDetail(resolution)
      sphere(1.0)
      resolution += 2
      translateX(2)
~~~



